[SN]TITLE[SN]
Bath Rugby: Dan Bowden and Nikola Matawalu out for rest of season

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Bath Rugby scrum-half Nikola Matawalu and utility back Dan Bowden will miss the rest of the season through injury.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Both players required surgery for their injuries, details of which have not been disclosed.
Fiji international Matawalu, 27, has made 10 appearances for the Premiership club since signing from Glasgow Warriors in December 2015.
Former Leicester and London Irish back Bowden, 29, has featured in only two games for Bath this season.
